  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The preset that opens the glass door between the player and the CuriosityEngine. vel_filter at 0.7 \u2014 play soft and the filter closes to a whisper, play hard and it opens to full brightness. Investigate mode responds to the LFO but your fingers control the light. Named for the Seance ghost's lament: 'the soul is locked behind glass.' This preset is the key.",
